{"tid":663633,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)屍殺列車 空中危機 白事可樂","createTime":"2018-05-13T12:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T18:07:45.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"efa51434b2b16f67cd4e9cd6616cb8110ed6d630","tid":663633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=9NWIzGp2NUhs3HN07PqVVAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=65a67fd8\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=9NWIzGp2NUhs3HN07PqVVAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f3993241\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=9NWIzGp2NUhs3HN07PqVVAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=9ea229dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e1/Train_to_Busan_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe1%2FTrain_to_Busan_Poster.jpg&h=2f61fae4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/2/2d/Flightplan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F2%2F2d%2FFlightplan.jpg&h=a7a54bda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9f/Newworldwarzpostersmall.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9f%2FNewworldwarzpostersmall.jpg&h=c21a4019&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/Non-Stop2014Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F87%2FNon-Stop2014Poster.jpg&h=54f12a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.韓國首爾一家證券公司的基金經理人徐碩宇，與妻子分居後因太過專注於工作，疏於照顧自己的女兒秀安。寂寞的秀安希望能在生日當天到釜山探母，碩宇為了答應女兒的生日願望，迫不得已而只好帶女兒，搭上從首爾往釜山的KTX高鐵列車前往。殊不知，一個神秘病毒開始擴散蔓延至整個國家，將感染者全部轉變成了嗜血喪屍，再通過瘋狂咬人傳播至更多的人。政府誤以為這是某種暴動示威而派軍隊阻止..<br />\n<br />\n2.女主角凱莉‧普雷是一位在柏林工作的航空工程師，不久前丈夫離奇的跌落窗外過世，留下她與六歲的女兒茱莉亞。為了將丈夫的靈柩運回美國。不過，在旅程的E-474客機上，起飛後，睡了一覺醒來凱莉卻發現女兒不見了，不但機上也沒人記得她帶了女兒上飛機，艙單裡也沒有茱莉亞的登機的紀錄。就在凱莉找回女兒的過程中，她也逐漸發現了一個巨大的陰謀&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.前聯合國調查員傑瑞&middot;藍恩與自己的妻子凱倫和兩個女兒瑞秋與康妮，愉快的在擁擠的費城市區公路上行車，但一分鐘內就有多架直升機從空中飛過，而新聞上一直在談論關於台灣爆發的狂犬病毒。突然間，公路前方發生了爆炸，而公路上執勤的警察當場被失控的垃圾車撞死，傑瑞跟隨垃圾車的行進路線離開公路，之後與一輛失控的救護車發生相撞。傑瑞與凱倫回過神來後，帶著女兒們丟下汽車逃跑，而廣場上也轉眼間出現了幾百名瘋狂咬人的殭屍，而傑瑞與家人逃離時親眼看到一名被殭屍咬到的人，在十二秒之內也淪為了一個殭屍，後來與家人開著一輛房車逃離了城市。不到兩小時，費城淪陷，美軍阻止殭屍的軍事行動全部以失敗告終...<br />\n<br />\n4.美國聯邦航空局的空中乘警比爾&middot;馬克斯，與同事傑克&middot;哈蒙在一架紐約飛往倫敦的波音767飛機上執行秘密反恐維安任務，而一名風情萬種的美麗熟女珍&middot;薩默斯換了靠窗位置而坐到比爾身邊。飛行期間有佳人相伴，原本比爾相當開心，但隨即狀況改變。比爾收到一系列神秘劫匪發送的威脅簡訊，對方不僅洞悉他的身份與嗜好，甚至威脅他如不要求美國政府以網路銀行向一個神秘帳戶轉入1.5億美元，就會每二十分鐘殺死一個乘客。比爾剛開始誤以為這是行事一向骯髒的哈蒙所搞的陰謀詭計，但通過會面他而檢查他的手機後發現不是他。為了秘密找出劫匪，比爾和始終坐在自己身旁而無嫌疑的珍、以及自己信任的一名女乘務員南希合作，通過監視系統來查出比爾收到簡訊期間、有誰動過手機..<br />\n<br />\n10 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=9NWIzGp2NUhs3HN07PqVVAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=807732d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=9NWIzGp2NUhs3HN07PqVVAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=364e4869\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec07cc686ed58e864a8089e7558114fdd784dfe","tid":663633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216074dab17b4f3282deed6f7b30429691312168","tid":663633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T13:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4347e8d7a93ab68783cb2652e1382f84ec94f66","tid":663633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69cd18d3df4fc8dc6dcfc24e43132fc226cfcac6","tid":663633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T16:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c581c227d4052f99b7631257fff3508bab67740e","tid":663633,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T18:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face